In [the current implementation](https://github.com/taiki-e/pin-project-lite/blob/bd4617ce80b9338e9db9a176157f7f31a0885cb3/src/lib.rs#L156-L157), an error will occur if the field has an attribute other than `#[pin]`.

```rust
pin_project! {
   #[derive(serde::Deserialize)]
   struct Struct1<T, U> {
       #[serde(default)] //~ ERROR 
       pinned: Option<T>,
       unpinned: U,
    }
}
```
